Today’s Spanish study session focused heavily on conversational travel Spanish, restaurant interactions, tourism vocabulary, recommendation phrases, and continued review of Pimsleur Unit 2 Lesson 9. Strong emphasis was placed on real-world conversational flow, practical sentence construction, and improving recall speed without relying on notes.

